{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_52_02",
  "title": "神崎莉央 2話 私のお願いを聞いてくれる……？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "……慰安旅行の一日目も終わりね\nみんなの世話を焼くので一日が終わった気がするわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…The first day of the company trip is over.\nI feel like the whole day's gone by just taking care of everyone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 8.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "まったく、どの子も自由気ままなんだから……\nすぐどこかに行っちゃうし、遠慮だってないし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good grief‚ every one of them is so free-spirited…\nThey just wander off somewhere‚ and they’ve got no sense of restraint…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 16.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お……お疲れ様です、莉央さん！　せっかくの慰安旅行\nなのにご迷惑ばかりお掛けしてしまいなんて謝罪を……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "G-good work‚ Rio-san! Even though it's supposed to be a relaxing trip‚\nwe've only caused you trouble‚ and I should apologize…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.690374279,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 25.2333330791
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！？　そこに居たのなら早く\n声を掛けなさいよ！　もう、盗み聞きなんて悪趣味だわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!? If you were there‚ you should have\ncalled out sooner! Seriously‚ eavesdropping is such a nasty habit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 33.9333330791
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "でも聞かれたなら、この際聞いてもらうわ。葵も相当\n気ままな性格だけど芽衣もfranさんも、いい勝負ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But since you’ve already heard‚ let me tell you. Aoi is quite\nfree-spirited‚ but Mei and Fran-san are a close match.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.0999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ……貴方一人であの子達をまとめ上げるのは難しい\nでしょうし、私がいて良かったわね。感謝してほしいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… managing those kids all by yourself would be tough‚\nso it's a good thing I'm here. You should be grateful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.7999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 53.0999997457
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "本当に感謝しています。そんな莉央さんにもゆっくり\nしてもらおうとおもてなしの用意をしたのでこちらへ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm truly grateful. I prepared some hospitality so that\nRio-san could also relax‚ so please come this way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.4651697477,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 60.3333330791
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "え、ちょ……ちょっと{user}さん！？\nもう夜なのにどこへ連れて行く気！？　今のは冗談……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ w-wait {user}-san!?\nWhere are you planning to take me when it's already night!? That was a joke…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.0999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 68.9666664124
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 68.9666664124
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cafe-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 69.2290474574
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 69.7999997457
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "……ここは、沖縄居酒屋？　素敵な雰囲気ね\nホテルのすぐ近くに、こんなお店があったなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…This is an Okinawan izakaya? What a lovely atmosphere.\nI didn't know there was a place like this right near the hotel.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.2999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん好みの店を探しておいたんですけど\n気に入ってもらえたなら良かったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I looked for a shop that would suit Rio-san's tastes‚\nso I'm glad you like it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.5666664124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 85.8666552225
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "年長者として、LizNoirのリーダーとして\nいつもみんなをよく見てくれて、ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As the eldest‚ as LizNoir's leader‚\nthank you for always looking after everyone so well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.4999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "……私のこと、そんな風に思ってくれていたのね\n年長者は、ちょっと余計だけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So you thought of me that way.\nEldest is a bit unnecessary though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.3666664124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 99.6333218891
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません。とにかくそんな莉央さんへのお礼です\n今晩は、心行くまで食事とお酒を楽しんで下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-sorry. Anyway‚ this is my thanks to Rio-san.\nTonight‚ please enjoy the food and drinks to your heart's content.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.4666664124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 108.8666552225
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、{user}さん\nそれじゃ、お言葉に甘えさせてもらおうかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ {user}-san.\nWell then‚ I'll take you up on your offer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.2333330791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 115.5999885558
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "でも明日の朝は早いんだから\nほどほどにしましょう。いいわね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But we have an early morning tomorrow‚\nso let's keep it moderate. Okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.4999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 122.1333330791
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ～、{user}さん、分かってる～？\n私は修学旅行の引率の先生じゃないのよ～！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey~ {user}-san‚ do you get it~?\nI'm not a school trip chaperone‚ you know~!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.1999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 133.833323415
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "大体、芽衣もfranも気まま過ぎるわよ～！\n普段、葵とこころだけでも手一杯だっていうのに！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Honestly‚ Mei and Fran are way too free-spirited~!\nJust dealing with Aoi and Kokoro is already a handful every day!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.7666764923,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね、分かります。あ、このラフテー\n美味しいですよ。良かったら莉央さんもどうぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ I understand. Oh‚ this rafute\nis delicious. Please try some‚ Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.8999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 151.1666664124
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "……うん、美味しい！　……大体せっかくの沖縄\nなんだから私だって本当はもっと自由にしたかったわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah‚ it's delicious! …Since we're in Okinawa after all‚\nI really wanted to be more free too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.6666664124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "私だって……私だってたまにはちょっとくらい\n羽目を外して遊んだっていいと思わない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I… I think it's okay for me‚ too‚ to let loose\nand have fun sometimes‚ don't you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.4999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 172.1333244323
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、俺が莉央さんに甘えてしまったばかりに\n明日はみんなのことは気にせず自由に過ごして下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry‚ because I relied on Rio-san too much.\nTomorrow‚ please spend your time freely without worrying about everyone!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.8666664124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 181.099991099
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "別に貴方を責めている訳ではないわ。私も私で\n勝手にあの子達の世話を焼いちゃってるだけだし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not blaming you or anything.\nI'm just taking care of those kids on my own…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.0666664124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "それに……なんだかんだ人の世話を焼くのは嫌いでは\nないのよね。もちろん、貴方の世話もよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides… one way or another‚ I don't dislike\ntaking care of people. Including you‚ of course.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.9999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 200.1333244323
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "……ねぇ。なんだか私ばっかり喋ってる気がするわ\n貴方も何か喋りなさいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey. I feel like I'm the only one talking.\nYou should say something too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 204.9666664124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 207.7666577656
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。何か面白い話をしてちょうだい。五秒以内よ\n五、四、三、二……何よ、その嫌そうな顔",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right. Tell me something interesting. Within five seconds.\nFive‚ four‚ three‚ two… What's with that disgusted look?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 213.2999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 215.0999997457
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "そうよね。こんな愚痴と無茶ぶりばかりの女と飲んでも\n楽しくないわよね。どうせ私なんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're right. Drinking with a woman who just complains and\nmakes unreasonable demands wouldn't be fun‚ right? I'm just…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 222.3666552227,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 226.8333122253
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっと待って下さい、そんなことないですよ\n俺だって、莉央さんと飲むのは凄く楽しいですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-wait a minute‚ that's not true at all.\nI also really enjoy drinking with Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
