      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_02-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "良かった……貴方に嫌われたら、その、困るわ\nねぇ、私のお願いを聞いてくれる……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good… if you disliked me‚ that would be‚ well‚ troublesome.\nHey‚ will you listen to my request…?",
        "id": ""
